premise_source_doc_sentence: He has received one Emmy for directing  (  2011  )  The Young and the Restless and was nominated for the same series in 2010 and 2013 .

The four main creators won the 2009 Emmy Award for Original Music and Lyrics for their work , while Ellis was bestowed a certificate of honor by the Emmy award 's Academy of Television Arts and Sciences , in June 2010 , for his contributions of original music and lyrics to the number .
